  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/cb81c81e061155eedc7b427b271b82ca.avif?t=1747752216\" width=408 height=178 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/26126f4d48ee3891f5e739fd27641d89.poster.avif?t=1747752216\" width=64 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/26126f4d48ee3891f5e739fd27641d89.webm?t=1747752216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Hop into the charming and unusual world of Frogbound, and play as the fabled Ser Hopper, a budding frog knight in search of adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the placid pond to the intricate mysteries below and above this strange world, you will slay countless enemies and uncover the cryptic secrets of the enigmatic old wizard toad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/38e47d315bb0260ca9e98af7fc0892a6.poster.avif?t=1747752216\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/38e47d315bb0260ca9e98af7fc0892a6.webm?t=1747752216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Frogbound: The Legend of Sir Hopper is a retro-style classic action-adventure implementing a retro aesthetic. Coded in Game Maker Studio and extremely lightweight, it is Stomaco Studio's debut title</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/500d90b9ec38ac9f77a5ec571806d4ff.avif?t=1747752216\" width=64 height=64 /></span>Sir Hopper, a versatile hero, masters the sword, bow, and arcane arts. To unleash his full potential, he seeks the proper relics that enhance his skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/4c401df22bde6da0cf393bda8850ec1d.poster.avif?t=1747752216\" width=418 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/4c401df22bde6da0cf393bda8850ec1d.webm?t=1747752216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/4c401df22bde6da0cf393bda8850ec1d.mp4?t=1747752216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/e3f0524bc53bf6236e2c6284738f1bc9.avif?t=1747752216\" width=64 height=64 /></span>Discover the Sextant, a relic that empowers Sir Hopper, equipping him with a deadly bow. Unleash deadly arrows upon foes from a distance, and use these arrows as stepping stones, enabling him to climb walls and gain newfound freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/e6bba685c39553ba5701f1d42ea776b3.poster.avif?t=1747752216\" width=418 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/e6bba685c39553ba5701f1d42ea776b3.webm?t=1747752216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/e6bba685c39553ba5701f1d42ea776b3.mp4?t=1747752216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/91d14b2b77f670d1819dac10040c1d7d.poster.avif?t=1747752216\" width=64 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/91d14b2b77f670d1819dac10040c1d7d.webm?t=1747752216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>With the Scroll in hand, Sir Hopper taps into the arcane, utilizing the surplus mana to float and propel himself higher, obtaining unlimited power and a double jump.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/58e8ff18873ea7d4ffd04646536ce78f.poster.avif?t=1747752216\" width=418 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/58e8ff18873ea7d4ffd04646536ce78f.webm?t=1747752216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/58e8ff18873ea7d4ffd04646536ce78f.mp4?t=1747752216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/1e790d56db30e3e00564a6c6fe2c4f77.apng?t=1747752216\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/1e790d56db30e3e00564a6c6fe2c4f77.poster.avif?t=1747752216\" class=\"bb_img\" width=160 height=64 /></picture></span>Equipped with the Broken Sword relic, Sir Hopper transforms into an unyielding Bulwark. His mighty slashes rend dungeon foes apart, unleashing devastating charged attacks and a formidable rush move,  that propels him through the levels with unstoppable force.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With these relics, Sir Hopper embodies a versatile champion, adapting to different playstyles and conquering the challenges that lie within the depths of the dungeon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEVELOPMENT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frogbound represents our first opus and acts as a codebase experiment, which we will keep working on for months, until we have reached a satisfactory framework to build the perfect metroidvania. Expect a feast of updates and play modes, for a snack-sized price!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TWISTED COMEDY</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/3a9fc3296a00df847d262a9c816ba0bf.apng?t=1747752216\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/3a9fc3296a00df847d262a9c816ba0bf.poster.avif?t=1747752216\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span>The adventure is ripe, and the mysteries abound: Sir Hopper is a young and brave adventurer, wielding a sharp blade, but maybe his mind is not as sharp as his weapons... Sir Hopper will discover a dark conspiracy, and slay the masters pulling the strings, he will face twisted horrors and empty husks of his brothers, and he will keep slaying, because slaying is always the answer... <i>right?<br></i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/51baaeffb8ad6f373556608869b95ab7.avif?t=1747752216\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras_big/51baaeffb8ad6f373556608869b95ab7.avif?t=1747752216 width=800 height=800 /></span></p>",
