vastating charged attacks and a formidable rush move,  that propels him through the levels with unstoppable force.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With these relics, Sir Hopper embodies a versatile champion, adapting to different playstyles and conquering the challenges that lie within the depths of the dungeon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEVELOPMENT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frogbound represents our first opus and acts as a codebase experiment, which we will keep working on for months, until we have reached a satisfactory framework to build the perfect metroidvania. Expect a feast of updates and play modes, for a snack-sized price!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TWISTED COMEDY</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/3a9fc3296a00df847d262a9c816ba0bf.apng?t=1747752216\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/3a9fc3296a00df847d262a9c816ba0bf.poster.avif?t=1747752216\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span>The adventure is ripe, and the mysteries abound: Sir Hopper is a young and brave adventurer, wielding a sharp blade, but maybe his mind is not as sharp as his weapons... Sir Hopper will discover a dark conspiracy, and slay the masters pulling the strings, he will face twisted horrors and empty husks of his brothers, and he will keep slaying, because slaying is always the answer... <i>right?<br></i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras/51baaeffb8ad6f373556608869b95ab7.avif?t=1747752216\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834250/extras_big/51baaeffb8ad6f37355660886